quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,97,"Say: \"Who was an enemy to Gabriel , so that he descended it on your heart/mind with God`s permission, confirming to what (is) between his hands, and (a) guidance and a good news to the believers"
  2,98,"Who was an enemy to God, and His angels, and His messengers, and Gabriel , and Michael , so then God (is) an enemy to the disbelievers"
  2,99,"And We had descended to you evidences signs/verses/evidences, and none disbelieves with it except the debauchers"
  2,100,"Is (it) whenever they promised a promise/contract a group of them broke it , but most of them do notbelieve"
  2,101,"And when a messenger came to them from at God confirming to what (is) with them, a group from those who were given The Book , discarded/rejected God`s Book behind their backs, as if they do not know"
  2,102,"And they followed what the devils read/recite on Soliman`s kingdom/ownership and Soliman did not disbelieve, and but the devils disbelieved. They teach the people the magic/sorcery and what was descended on the two kings/angels Harut and Marutat Babylon, and they (B) do not teach from anyone until they (B) say: \"But we are a test , so do not disbelieve\". So they learn from them (B) what they separate with it between the human/man and his wife, and they are not with harming with it from anyone except with God`s permission. And they learn what harms them and does not benefit them, and they had known for who (E) bought it, (there is) no share of blessing/fortune for him in the end (other life), and how bad (E) (is) what they bought/volunteered with it themselves, if they were knowing"
  2,103,"And if they had believed and feared and obeyed, then a reward (E) from at God, (is) better if they were knowing"